{"tid":1287781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高EQ回應Haters　網民大讚ROLAND：不愧是第一牛郎","createTime":"2019-07-05T10:52:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T11:07:34.000Z","uid":25345,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b6545b1228cb96ba6e9296ded94820931ac0be1a","tid":1287781,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T10:52:30.000Z","msg":"大家還記得早前日本爆紅的「歌舞伎町帝王」ROLAND嗎？作為年賺三億円（約2157萬港幣）的日本第一牛郎，除了外型別樹一格外，令他成名的就是結合幽默與極度自戀特色的金句。<br />\nROLAND名言：「世上只有兩種男人，就是我，及我以外的男人。」 （ROLANDofficialsite）<br />\n<br />\nROLAND名言：「世上只有兩種男人，就是我，及我以外的男人。」 （ROLANDofficialsite）<br />\n<br />\n笑對Haters惡意留言<br />\n<br />\n作為日本第一牛郎，再加上極度自戀的個性，自然惹來不少Haters，也有不少人在他個人Twitter留言評擊他。<br />\n<br />\n不過對於接客經驗豐富的ROLAND來說，應付Haters似乎沒有難度，亦從中爆出不少鬼馬兼自戀的新金句，近日亦引起不少網民熱烈討論。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2990559/org/bffb5c303217bb9161d8984547a39f8a.jpg/0JoZ2l16GaYJAhaqSbbQ4DTQJJidimqLzckeRs3JHkY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2990559%2Forg%2Fbffb5c303217bb9161d8984547a39f8a.jpg%2F0JoZ2l16GaYJAhaqSbbQ4DTQJJidimqLzckeRs3JHkY&h=9b9a2e5c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2990572/org/03b02bd4e3496e7c75e77899f046b7e5.jpg/ECmJKTvpfg2W9nmVASbwco5tkMmfo_sDoW-hgqFvoYI\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2990572%2Forg%2F03b02bd4e3496e7c75e77899f046b7e5.jpg%2FECmJKTvpfg2W9nmVASbwco5tkMmfo_sDoW-hgqFvoYI&h=9e28d114&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2990564/org/ee51313d650d556a9e4547b077862aae.jpg/CbsI6KI2PUT689yMiS2vDdK3L5hcaGNjg-DhRoPg4UY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2990564%2Forg%2Fee51313d650d556a9e4547b077862aae.jpg%2FCbsI6KI2PUT689yMiS2vDdK3L5hcaGNjg-DhRoPg4UY&h=428a8a5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2990565/org/5ee9c35eb74c681948bfdbb9f2daa683.jpg/